OL,3,CMet Office warns of rise in extreme UK
OL,4,Cweather, as 2023 second hottest year
OL,5,Cever
OL,7,FThe Met Office also confirmed 2023 was
OL,8,Fthe warmest year on record for Wales
OL,9,Fand Northern Ireland, as ITV News
OL,10,FHealth & Science Correspondent Martin
OL,11,FStew explains
OL,13,FOur weather is becoming more extreme
OL,14,Fmore often, according to the Met
OL,15,FOffice's State of Climate report.
OL,17,FIt compares weather data and events
OL,18,Ffrom last year with statistics dating
OL,19,Fback to the 19th century.
